title: 74 What a Musical Genius Can Teach You About World Class Music Production (CJ Baran Reveals All)
description:
He lived 20 ft. from me the whole time...
Before he spent his 20th birthday he used social media to leverage a record deal. As a teenager he opened for Jusin Bieber and Miley Cyrus. To many, he achieved the height of fame and fortune. But something was missing...
Find out the rest of the story at at www.lewishowes.com/74
author: podcast@schoolofgreatness.com (Lewis Howes)
